--Install AWS CLI on Windows using instructions given in the following link:
--https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/install-windows.html#install-msi-on-windows

--configure using following commands:

$aws configure

AWS Access Key ID [None]: AKIAIOSFODNN7EXAMPLE
AWS Secret Access Key [None]: wJalrXUtnFEMI/K7MDENG/bPxRfiCYEXAMPLEKEY
Default region name [None]: us-west-2
Default output format [None]: json

Note : To get Key ID and Secret Access to enter above follow below instructions:

AWS Tookit icon can be seen after installation. select preferences from drop down menu and enter:
Access Key ID and Secret Access Key, downloaded from "My Security Credentials" --> "Access Keys" --> Create New Access Key.


--check if you able to connect to your AWS account and access your services:

$aws s3 ls
